high_descs: Turn around, go forward past the stove, turn to face the counter on the right.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn left, go to the fridge, turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the spoon in the mug on the top shelf.
Pick up the mug with the spoon from the top shelf of the fridge.
Turn right, move to the counter before the stove, face the counter on the left.
Put the mug with spoon on the counter left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with spoon in it on the counter left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk up to the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the metal spoon that is on the counter to the left of the oven.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the spoon handle down inside the white mug that is on the top shelf inside the fridge.
Pick up the white mug with the spoon inside of it and close the fridge door.
Turn right and walk over to the dishwasher, turn left to face the counter.
Put the white mug with the spoon inside of it on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon inside of it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, then turn right to face the counter, to the right of the oven.
Pick up the spoon on the counter, to the left of the butter knives.
Turn left and go to the fridge ahead of you.
Put the spoon in the mug, on the top shelf of the fridge.
Pick up the mug with the spoon in it.
Turn right, go straight, then turn left at the dishwasher.
Put the mug on the counter, in front of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Move to the left of the stove
Pick up a spoon from the counter
Move to the fridge to the left of you
Put spoon inside a cup
Pick up cup from the fridge
Move to the counter to the left of the stove
put cup on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with spoon on the counter to  the left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk until you get to the counter on your right with the utensils on it.
Pick up the spoon directly to the left of the pear.
Turn left and walk until you reach the fridge.
Place the spoon in the white mug on the top shelf of the fridge.
Grab the mug that you placed the spoon in.
Turn to your right and walk back to the counter that you got the spoon from.
Place the mug on the front of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a spoon in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go straight pass the oven and turn right towards the counter.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Turn left go towards the Fridge and open the fridge.
Place the spoon in the Cup on the first rack of the fridge.
Take out the cup with the spoon and close the fridge.
Turn right and go towards the counter and then turn left in front of the counter.
Place the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Bring a white cup from the Fridge to the Counter.
